document_data.name: Temple of Sehanine
document_data.inhabitants: Inhabitants of the Temple of Sehanine
document_data.mainbody: The '''Temple of Sehanine''' was a temple to [[Sehanine Moonbow]] in [[Leuthilspar]] on the island of [[Evermeet]].
document_data.Structure: The temple was a two-spire construction and, in [[1369 DR]], was run by [[Soliania Durothil]].
